workflowProcessDefs.name: WGS Library Construction Hyper Prep UMI
Cell Free Library Construction Hyper Prep UMI

workflowStepDefs.name: Initial Scan
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Scan all parent source SM-IDs to cross check against samples in XTR ticket

workflowStepDefs.name: Prep Reagents
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Before starting, confirm all reagents have been prepared: Buffer AL incubated at 56C to dissolve precipitate, if needed 100% Ethanol added to Buffer AW1 100% Ethanol added to Buffer AW2

workflowStepDefs.name: Prep workspace
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Disinfect lab space and sample rack.

workflowStepDefs.name: Incubate Samples
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Collect samples for extraction from +4C fridge or freezer. If samples are frozen, incubate at 37C for 10 minutes. Remove from incubator and place on ice.

workflowStepDefs.name: Transfer to microcentrifuge tube
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Label one microcentrifuge tube for each sample. Pipet 20ul of proteinase K into the tube. Add 200ul of blood to each microcentrifuge tube. Add 200ul of Buffer AL to each microcentrifuge tube.

workflowStepDefs.name: Mix AL
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Mix by pulse vortexing for 15 seconds.

workflowStepDefs.name: Incubate AL
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Incubate at 56C for 10 minutes.

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge AL
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Briefly centrifuge the tube to remove drops from the lid.

workflowStepDefs.name: Add Ethanol
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 200ul of 100% ethanol to the sample.

workflowStepDefs.name: Mix Ethanol
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Mix by pulse vortexing for 15 seconds, then briefly spin down.

workflowStepDefs.name: Transfer to spin column
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Apply the mixture to the QIAamp Mini spin column in a 2ml collection tube

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge Ethanol
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Spin at 6000 x g for 1 minute.

workflowStepDefs.name: Move Column After Ethanol
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Place the column in a clean 2ml collection tube and discard the tube with the filtrate.

workflowStepDefs.name: Add AW1
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 500ul Buffer AW1 to the column.

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge AW1
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Spin at 6,000 x g for 1 minute.

workflowStepDefs.name: Move Column After AW1
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Place the column in a clean 2ml collection tube and discard the tube with the filtrate.

workflowStepDefs.name: Add AW2
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 500ul Buffer AW2 to the column.

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge AW2
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Spin at full speed (20,000 x g) for 3 minutes.

workflowStepDefs.name: Move Column After AW2
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Place the column in a clean 2ml collection tube and discard the tube with the filtrate.

workflowStepDefs.name: Second Centrifuge After AW2
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Spin at full speed for 1 minute.

workflowStepDefs.name: Second Move Column After AW2
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Place the column in a clean 1.5ml microcentrifuge tube and discard the tube with the filtrate.

workflowStepDefs.name: Add AE
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 200ul Buffer AE to the column and incubate at room temperature for 1 minute.

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge AE
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Spin at 6,000 x g for 1 minute.

workflowStepDefs.name: Transfer to matrix
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Transfer the eluate to a labeled 0.5ml barcoded 2D matrix tube.

workflowStepDefs.name: Store
workflowStepDefs.instructions: If necessary, store at +4C until ready to proceed to Plating.

workflowProcessDefs.name: DNA and RNA from Cell Pellets

bucketEntryEvaluator.workflows: DNA and RNA from Cell Pellets

workflowStepDefs.name: Initial Scan
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Scan all parent source SM-IDs to cross check against samples in XTR ticket

workflowStepDefs.name: Prep Reagents
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Before starting, confirm all reagents have been prepared: RLT+ w/B-ME, Proteinase K, Buffer RPE w/EtOH, Buffer RDD w/RNase-Free DNase I, Buffer FRN w/Isopropanol, Buffer AW1, and Buffer AW2 w/EtOH.

workflowStepDefs.name: Wash PBS
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Pellet in existing tube and wash w/PBS (x2)?

workflowStepDefs.name: Re-suspend
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Re-suspend in PBS (3mL)

workflowStepDefs.name: Transfer Cells to Cryovial
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Transfer to 2mL Cryovial (half the volume, 1.5mL)

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge Cryovial
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Centrifuge (5 min @ 300g) and remove supernatant.

workflowStepDefs.name: Add RLT+ w/B-ME
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 350uL or 600uL buffer RLT+ w/B-ME

workflowStepDefs.name: Transfer to QIAshredder
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Transfer lysate directly into a QIAshredder spin column placed in a 2 ml collection tube.

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge QIAshredder
workflowStepDefs.instructions: centrifuge for 2 min at maximum speed

workflowStepDefs.name: Transfer to DNA Spin Column
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Transfer the homogenized lysate to an AllPrep DNA spin column placed in a 2 ml collection tube (supplied).

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge DNA Spin Column
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Centrifuge for 30 s at full speed (max 20,000 x g)

workflowStepDefs.name: Move DNA Column
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Place AllPrep DNA spin column in a new 2 ml collection tube (supplied), and set aside. Store at room temperature (1525C) or at 4C for later DNA purification.

workflowStepDefs.name: Transfer Flow-through to 2 ml Tube
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Transfer the flow-through to a new 2 ml microcentrifuge tube (not supplied) for RNA purification.

workflowStepDefs.name: Add Proteinase K
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 50uL or 80uL Proteinase K to flow-through.

workflowStepDefs.name: Add 100% ethanol
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 200uL or 350uL 100% ethanol to the flowthrough

workflowStepDefs.name: Incubate
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Incubate for 10 min at room temperature.

workflowStepDefs.name: Add 100% ethanol
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 400uL or 750uL 100% ethanol to the flowthrough

workflowStepDefs.name: Transfer to RNA Spin Column 1
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Transfer 700uL to RNA spin column.

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge RNA Spin Column 1
workflowStepDefs.instructions: centrifuge for 15 s at full speed (max 20,000 x g).

workflowStepDefs.name: Move Column After Transfer to RNA Spin Column 1
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Place the column in a clean 2ml collection tube and discard the tube with the filtrate.

workflowStepDefs.name: Transfer to RNA Spin Column 2
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Transfer 700uL to RNA spin column in 2 ml collection tube (supplied).

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge RNA Spin Column 2
workflowStepDefs.instructions: centrifuge for 15 s at full speed (max 20,000 x g).

workflowStepDefs.name: Move Column After Transfer to RNA Spin Column 2
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Place the column in a clean 2ml collection tube and discard the tube with the filtrate.

workflowStepDefs.name: Transfer to RNA Spin Column 3
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Transfer remaining volume to RNA spin column in 2 ml collection tube (supplied).

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge RNA Spin Column 3
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Centrifuge for 15 s at full speed (max 20,000 x g).

workflowStepDefs.name: Move Column After Transfer to RNA Spin Column 3
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Place the column in a clean 2ml collection tube and discard the tube with the filtrate.

workflowStepDefs.name: Add RPE 1
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 500uL Buffer RPE to the RNA spin column

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge RNA Spin Column RPE 1
workflowStepDefs.instructions: centrifuge for 15 s at full speed (max 20,000 x g).

workflowStepDefs.name: Move Column After RPE 1
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Place the column in a clean 2ml collection tube and discard the tube with the filtrate.

workflowStepDefs.name: Add Buffer RDD w/DNase I
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 80uL Buffer RDD w/DNase I to RNA spin column.

workflowStepDefs.name: Incubate
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Incubate on the benchtop (20-30C) for 15 min.

workflowStepDefs.name: Add Buffer FRN
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 500uL Buffer FRN to RNA spin column.

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge RNA Spin Column
workflowStepDefs.instructions: centrifuge for 15 s at full speed (max 20,000 x g) and ***save flow-through***.

workflowStepDefs.name: Move RNA Column After FRN
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Place AllPrep RNA spin column in a new 2ml collection tube (supplied).

workflowStepDefs.name: Transfer Flow-through to RNA Column
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Transfer flow-through to RNA spin column.

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge RNA Spin Column
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Centrifuge for 15 s at full speed (max 20,000 x g).

workflowStepDefs.name: Add RPE 2
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 500uL Buffer RPE to the RNA spin column

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge RNA Spin Column RPE 2
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Centrifuge for 15 s at full speed (max 20,000 x g).

workflowStepDefs.name: Move Column After RPE 2
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Place the column in a clean 2ml collection tube and discard the tube with the filtrate.

workflowStepDefs.name: Add 100% ethanol
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 500uL 100% ethanol to the spin column

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge RNA Spin Column Dry
workflowStepDefs.instructions: centrifuge for 2 minutes at full speed to dry membrane

workflowStepDefs.name: Move Column After Dry
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Move RNA spin column to a new 1.5 ml collection tube

workflowStepDefs.name: Add Water
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 50uL water directly to the spin column membrane

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge RNA Spin Column Water
workflowStepDefs.instructions: centrifuge for 1 min at 8000g to elute

workflowStepDefs.name: Transfer RNA To Microcentrifuge
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Transfer RNA to microcentrifuge tube.

workflowStepDefs.name: Transfer RNA To Matrix
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Transfer from microcentrifuge tube to 2D matrix tube

workflowStepDefs.name: Add AW1
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 350uL AW1 to DNA spin column

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge DNA Spin Column AW1
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Centrifuge for 15 s at full speed (max 20,000 x g).

workflowStepDefs.name: Move Column After AW1
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Move DNA spin column to a new 1.5 ml collection tube and discard flowthrough

workflowStepDefs.name: Add Buffer AW1 w/Proteinase K
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 60uL Buffer AW1 w/ 20uL Proteinase K to DNA spin column

workflowStepDefs.name: Incubate
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Incubate at room temperature for 5 min

workflowStepDefs.name: Add AW1
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 350uL AW1 to DNA spin column

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge DNA Spin Column AW1
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Centrifuge for 15 s at >=8000 x g

workflowStepDefs.name: Move Column After AW1
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Move DNA spin column to a new 1.5 ml collection tube and discard flow-through

workflowStepDefs.name: Add AW2
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 500 l Buffer AW2 to the DNA spin column

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge DNA Spin Column AW2
workflowStepDefs.instructions: centrifuge for 2 min at full speed

workflowStepDefs.name: Move Column After AW2
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Move DNA spin column to a new 1.5 ml collection tube and discard flow-through

workflowStepDefs.name: Dry DNA Spin Column Membrane
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Spin DNA spin column for 1 min at full speed (max 20,000 x g)

workflowStepDefs.name: Move Column After Dry
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Move DNA spin column to a new 1.5 ml collection tube and discard flow-through

workflowStepDefs.name: Add EB
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Add 100uL Buffer EB to the spin column

workflowStepDefs.name: Incubate
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Incubate at RT 1min

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge DNA Spin Column After Incubation
workflowStepDefs.instructions: centrifuge for 1 min at 8000 x g

workflowStepDefs.name: Transfer DNA To Microcentrifuge
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Transfer DNA to microcentrifuge tube

workflowStepDefs.name: Transfer DNA Microcentrifuge to Matrix
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Transfer from microcentrifuge tube to 2D matrix tube

workflowProcessDefs.name: DNA and RNA for Frozen Tissue - AllPrep

bucketEntryEvaluator.workflows: DNA and RNA for Frozen Tissue - AllPrep

workflowStepDefs.name: Extract to DNA and RNA From Stool
Initial Scan
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Scan parent source CO-ID. Press "validate barcodes" to cross check against samples in XTR ticket. Ensure control samples have been added to Mercury. Eppendorf 12x8 Box Well Format

workflowStepDefs.name: Prep Reagents
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Heat Buffer PW1 to 55C for 30 minutes or more - prime heated buffer PW1 with 1:100 of BME (10ul BME per 1ml of PW1). Aliquot based off # of samples. - Add required EtOH to RPE, AW1, and AW2. Plate Buffer EB in a PCR plate and heat to 70C prior to DNA Elution. - Prepare reagent S-Blocks for all Bravo protocols.

workflowStepDefs.name: Transfer material to PowerBead Plate
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Aliquot sample to PowerBead Plate and update the masses in the spreadsheet if needed. - Checking the checkbox next to mass removed will deplete the sample and any mass in source will be transferred.

workflowStepDefs.name: Bead Beating
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Shake PowerBead plate @ 20 Hz for 5 minutes. Once complete, rotate samples 180 degrees and repeat step.

workflowStepDefs.name: Spin
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Centrifuge PowerBead plate for 6 minutes @4,500 x g

workflowStepDefs.name: Transfer Supernatent to IRS S-Block
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Scan container ID on bead plate and container ID on IRS S-Block . Transfer ~650ul for supernatant. - Seal and vortex gently (no splashing)

workflowStepDefs.name: Incubate
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Incubate for 1 min at room temperature.

workflowStepDefs.name: Centrifuge IRS Lysate S-Block
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Centrifuge IRS lysate S-Block for 6 minutes @4,500 x g

workflowStepDefs.name: Bravo: IRS supernatant transfer to C4 in new S-Block
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Start Script: 1) Qiagen AllPrep Initial Filter to transfer ~450ul of supernatant to new C4 Lysate S-Block

workflowStepDefs.name: Bravo: S-Block to AllPrep Filter Plate
workflowStepDefs.instructions: **TNA SPLIT STEP** Scan barcodes for sample transfer to All Prep Filter Plate (DNA) on RNA FT S-Block

workflowStepDefs.name: Bravo: RNA FT S-Block to RNA Filter Plate
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Start Script: 2) Qiagen AllPrep RNA Isolation Washes. Scan barcode of RNA flow through S-Block to barcode of RNA Filter Plate.

workflowStepDefs.name: Bravo: RNA Isolation
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Return RNA Filter plate to deck and continue Bravo script.

workflowStepDefs.name: Bravo: RNA Filter To Elution
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Start Bravo Script: 3) Qiagen AllPrep RNA Final Elution using the samples in RNAeasy Filter Plate

workflowStepDefs.name: Bravo: RNA Elution To Final Rack
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Link Elution Plate to Final Rack

workflowStepDefs.name: Bravo: DNA Isolation
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Start Bravo Script: 4) Qiagen AllPrep DNA Isolation Washes using the samples in the stored DNA AllPrep Filter Plate

workflowStepDefs.name: Bravo: DNA Filter To Elution
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Start Bravo Script: 5) Qiagen AllPrep DNA final elution using the samples in AllPrep Filter Plate and heated EB buffer plate.

workflowStepDefs.name: Bravo: DNA Elution To Final Rack
workflowStepDefs.instructions: Link Elution Plate to Final Rack
